'''Paal Buogl''' ONH (baan 1822 an ded 24 Aktuoba 1865) a wahn a di [[Nashinal Iiro|Nashinal Iiro]] dem a [[Jamieka|Jamieka]] a wehn a wah [[Baptis Choch|Baptis]] diikan. A im weh liid wah gruup a piipl frah [[Morant Bie|Morant Bie]] ina [[Sin Tamas Parish, Jumieka|Sin Tamas Parish]] we ena-pruotes fi get jostis ah fier triitment ina 1865. Dis ya pruotes eh-ton big-big an a we wi nou nuo az di [[Morant Bie Ribeliyan|Morant Bie Ribelian]]. <ref name =http://scholar.library.miami.edu>[http://scholar.library.miami.edu/emancipation/jamaica4.htm "The Cause of the Morant Bay Rebellion: 1865", Miami Library website.]</ref> Nou afta ih da-liid di ribelian, di [[British Empaya|British]] aatariti deh kiapcha im ah eng im fronta di [[Morant Bie Kuotous|Morant Bie Kuotous]].

Paal Buogl a weh gud-gud fren wid wah neda Baptis palitishan man niem [[Jaaj Wiliam Gaadn|Jaaj Wiliam Gaadn]] uu weh-uon nof lan. A im eh-elp mek Buogl get apaint az di diikan fi Stuoni Got Baptis Choch (Stony Gut Baptist Church) ina 1864. Ina Aagos 1865, Gaadn go tu di British Gobna, Eduad Jan Ier, bout di iipa anfier triitment ah opreshan gens di nigrodem. Deh taim de Buogl ena-fuokos pah ou ih kuda mek laif beta fi di puo piipldem.

